2%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E-IE%EF%BC%89-2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实例（仅适用于 IE）</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">调用程序</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%85%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E-IE%EF%BC%89-3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实例（仅适用于 IE）</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#VBScript-%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">VBScript 条件语句</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">条件语句</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#If%E2%80%A6Then%E2%80%A6Else\"><span class=\"toc-text\">If…Then…Else</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%85%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E-IE%EF%BC%89-4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实例（仅适用于 IE）</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#If%E2%80%A6Then%E2%80%A6ElseIf\"><span class=\"toc-text\">If…Then…ElseIf</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%85%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E-IE%EF%BC%89-5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实例（仅适用于 IE）</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Select-Case\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Select Case</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%85%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E-IE%EF%BC%89-6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实例（仅适用于 IE）</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href